
-> Binder (the android.os.Binder class) is the base entry point for all Binder IPC(Inter Process Communications).
-> ConstraintLayout is best for nesting complex UI with performance in mind.
-> Activity or Fragment handles runtime permissions via requestPermissions() and onRequestPermissionsResult().
-> Window → ViewRootImpl → View hierarchy` handles drawing the UI. This component is responsible for drawing the UI on screen.
-> WorkManager allows background work that guarantees execution even after app kill or device restart.